# CalmStudio is built as part of the FINOS architecture-as-code monorepo.
# The authoritative dependency lockfile is the repository-root package-lock.json,
# which resolves calm-studio's packages/* and apps/* as npm workspaces and applies
# the central security `overrides` (e.g. cookie, undici). Every CI workflow installs
# from that root lockfile via `npm ci`.
#
# A separate nested lockfile here is never installed by CI and silently drifts from
# the central build (it does not inherit the root overrides, so it re-introduces
# already-patched CVEs). Keep it out of version control so the root lockfile remains
# the single source of truth. Run npm commands from the repository root.
package-lock.json
